in Mexico thought he was home and dry - but

00:02:28.390 --> 00:02:31.670
he didn't reckon on Pancho the local sealion.

00:02:31.670 --> 00:02:36.760
Chef Yvan Mucharrz had been taken on the fishing
trip by Mike 'The Griz' Ritz during filming

00:02:36.760 --> 00:02:41.750
